## Usage

Trigger with phrases like:
- "Test form validation on [URL]"
- "Check validation errors for this form"
- "Verify error messages are displayed"

The skill will:
1. Navigate to form
2. Test all validation rules systematically
3. Capture screenshots of error states
4. Generate comprehensive report

